            <description><![CDATA[<div class="quote"><blockquote><font size="2"><a href="https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&goto=findpost&pid=28233172&ptid=1100932" target="_blank"><font color="#999999">choice 发表于 2015-3-3 11:33</font></a></font><br>
kinect完全靠camera，这头盔上一堆主动sensor，定位完全不一样啊</blockquote></div><br>
